SAUTE first 8 ingredients in hot olive oil in a large Dutch oven until meat is browned. DRAIN and return meat mixture to Dutch oven. STIR in cocoa and next 13 ingredients; bring to a boil. Cover, reduce heat, and simmer, stirring occasionally, 1 1/2 hours. COMBINE sour cream and next 8 ingredients; chill. Serve with chili. Top with shredded cheese, if desired.